a:2:{s:7:"content";s:1534:"<h2>Suburban Philadelphia's focus group and product testing facility in historic Bucks County!</h2>
<p>Located in historic and beautiful Bucks County Pennsylvania, this upscale market research facility features flexible product testing space, focus group suite and spacious client lounge. With an average tenure of 15 years, the staff executes product tests flawlessly. Less than one hour from the Philadelphia International Airport with an abundance of shopping, accommodations and dining options. We also offer free transportation to and from the airport to our facility.</p>
<h3>Location</h3>
<ul>
<li>Represents the Northeastern portion of the Philadelphia MSA</li>
<li>60 minutes from Philadelphia International Airport</li>
<li>Many hotels, restaurants and shopping within a 5-mile radius</li>
<li>Less than 1 hour from Trenton, New Jersey and Wilmington, Delaware</li>
</ul>
<h3>Features</h3>
<ul>
<li>Large Multi-Purpose Room (30' x 44') with seating for 30 CLT respondents.</li>
<li>2 private flex spaces adjacent to MRP - ideal for peel off IDIs</li>
<li>Test Kitchen (38' x 15') with commercial refrigerator (46cf) and freezer (46cf), 10 microwaves, 3 countertop convection ovens and more</li>
<li>Large Focus Group room (24' x 20') with large client observation room (24'x18')</li>
<li>Focus Group Suite also includes a Client lounge and 2 additional private flex spaces.</li>
<li>Complimentary Reckner video streaming available</li>
<li>In home use testing. Ability to ship out iHUT products from the facility.</li>
</ul>";s:12:"content_meta";N;}